Matthew Gray Gubler -LRB- born March 9 , 1980 -RRB- is an American actor , director , fashion model and painter .
He is best known for his role as criminal profiler Dr. Spencer Reid in the CBS television show Criminal Minds -LRB- 2005 -- present -RRB- , of which he has also directed ten episodes .
Gubler has appeared in The Life Aquatic with Steve Zissou , -LRB- 500 -RRB- Days of Summer , Life After Beth , Suburban Gothic , and as the voice of Simon in Alvin and the Chipmunks and its three sequels .